🐗 Stomper Wendy spotted a wild boar at Bishan-Ang Mo Kio Park on Wednesday (April 15), at around 9.24pm.
Do you think is possible that they come all the way from Indonesia?

Did anyone notice one thing... since the covid ,  lot of wild animals appear. .MONKEYS,  HORSE, WILD BOAR, SNAKES,  BIRDS.......... . ARE HUMAN BEING GOING TO VANISH?  ANIMALS are taking over the world? ??
now that is what i call a babi kontol
